  </a>
</div>

## Installation

```bash
$ Python3 -m pip install img2ansi
```

## Features
- ASCII convertion
- BRAILE/DOT convertion
- Block convertion
- Custom ASCII character set
- Invert character set
- No echo **/** echo to terminal
- Resize of image
- Save to a file
- True color

## ANSI support
- Bold
- Blink
- True color Foreground
- True color Background 

## Todo
- [x] Simple Ascii convertion
